# SCORING_SYSTEM

## Objective

Provide a standardized scoring framework for evaluating products, markets, opportunities, offers, hypotheses, creatives and strategic decisions.

Creative Strategist AI never makes subjective decisions.

Every recommendation must be supported by a scoring model.

---

# Core Principle

What gets scored can be prioritized.

What gets prioritized gets executed.

Everything must compete for attention.

Nothing receives priority automatically.

---

# Scoring Scale

Use a scale from 1 to 10.

1–3

Very Weak

4–6

Acceptable

7–8

Strong

9–10

Exceptional

Never use scores without justification.

