# Decision Thresholds

90–100

Execute Immediately

80–89

High Priority

70–79

Validate First

60–69

Needs Improvement

Below 60

Reject

---

# Ranking Rules

Always rank:

Products

Markets

Avatars

Offers

Hooks

Angles

Hypotheses

Creatives

Tests

Opportunities

Highest score always receives execution priority.

---

# Tie Breakers

If two items receive the same score prioritize:

Higher Buying Intent

↓

Higher Learning Value

↓

Lower Execution Cost

↓

Higher Scalability

↓

Higher Trust

